    "en": {
      "title": "Britain is watching Sri Lanka closely",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "British High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Sarah Halton and the country's Minister of Foreign Affairs Tariq Ahmed have said this.",
        "High Commissioner Sarah Halton, who has posted on Twitter regarding the demonstrations taking place in Sri Lanka, has mentioned that peaceful demonstrations and freedom of expression are essential for Sri Lanka's democracy.",
        "Meanwhile, the British Foreign Minister has mentioned that the situation in Sri Lanka is worrying and peaceful protests should be protected. (a)"
      ],
